name: Tirupati Engineering
overview: Established in the year 1982, we, “Tirupati Engineering”, are among the most respectable organizations, engaged in manufacturing and supplying a comprehensive range of Batch Printing Machine. Under this range, we offer Corton Batch Printing Machine, Label Batch Print Machine, Label & Corton Batch Printing Machine, Semi Label Gumming Machine and Winding Rewinding Machine. All our products are designed and developed in accordance with international quality norms & standards, using high-grade raw material and latest technology. These products are widely appreciated by the customers for their corrosion & abrasion resistance, sturdy construction, low maintenance, less power consumption and longer service life. All our products are widely demanded
